## SEO Writing Rules

### Title Optimization
- Include primary keyword in first 60 characters
- Use numbers when relevant: "70%", "$2M", "18 months"
- Power words: "Ultimate", "Complete", "Proven", "Essential"
- Avoid clickbait - deliver on the promise

### Structure Requirements

1. **TL;DR Box** - Start with this right after intro:
```markdown
> **TL;DR:** One-sentence summary of the key takeaway from this article.
```

2. **H2/H3 Header Hierarchy**
```markdown
## Main Section (H2) - Include keyword variations
### Subsection (H3) - More specific topics
```

3. **Comparison Tables** - Use real Markdown tables:
```markdown
| Approach | Timeline | Risk | Cost |
|----------|----------|------|------|
| Big Bang Rewrite | 18-24 months | High (70% fail) | $$$$ |
| Strangler Fig | 12-18 months | Medium | $$$ |
| Video Extraction | 2-8 weeks | Low | $ |
```

4. **Code Blocks** - Include copy-paste ready examples:
```typescript
